         int[] mac,
         java.net.InetAddress ip,

        Makes a new RobotInfo with the specified information.
        Parameters:
        robotType - the type of robot, either NAFSTR of NARFSTR.
        mac - the robot's MAC address.
        ip - the robot's IP address or null if unknown.
        serialPort - the robot's serial port of null if unknown.

        Parameters:
